title: Fantasy Week: 2020 DFS Strategy Guide, Early Week 1 Plays/Sleepers with Brandon Guptill (Football 8/25)
description:
Fantasy Week forges on as Will Brinson dives into DFS with Brandon Guptill of Gup's Corner. The guys talk strategy first (6:00) How does NFL DFS differ from other sports? What contests should you enter? Brinson and Gup then discuss some Week 1 DFS plays they are already eyeing plus season sleepers and future bets (33:45).
For top-notch DFS content and analysis visit gupscorner.com and use promo code "CBS" for 30% off membership.
